Author: Alright#0419
Content:
found a way to reliably create stuck swaps. 
start a swap
turn the phone off
wait a minute, so swap is at 2/3
turn phone back on 
hit red button that clears seed
restore the wallet 
swap will be stuck at 2/3 with seemingly no way to recover the funds sent
